<span id="more"></span>
<h2 id="拉取仓库"><a href="#拉取仓库" class="headerlink" title="拉取仓库"></a>拉取仓库</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git remote add origin git@github.com:foxscalliom/test.git</span><br><span class="line">git branch -M main</span><br><span class="line">git push -u origin main</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
